interpretation: The "woman factory worker" card represents hard work, productivity, and efficiency. This card suggests that you may need to focus on your work or career, putting in the time and effort needed to achieve your goals. You may also need to be more practical and organized, developing a plan and sticking to it. This card can also indicate a need to work with others, as teamwork and collaboration will be key to your success. Stay focused, be persistent, and trust in your abilities to get the job done.
